data.description: Vintage and Traditional Home with Detached Garage Apartment located just off Waynesville's Main Street. The stately two story home features 4BR's/2BA's. hardwood floors, 9 ft ceilings, formal living room with wood burning fireplace, traditional staircase to 2nd floor,  dining room, kitchen with island, spacious laundry area, and cozy den/family room, with wood burning fireplace. 2nd floor boasts 4 spacious bedrooms and full bath. The  classic home also features covered traditional front porch and mature gorgeous landscaping with flat yard space. The detached garage apartment features 2BR's/1BA perfect for rental or overflow quarters. Embrace the chance to make this house your own, incorporating modern touches while maintaining its upscale vintage feel. Plus, enjoy the convenience of being less than 5 minutes to Downtown Waynesville and just 30 minutes to Asheville. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a piece of history and charm in one.
